                            <comment id="13274709" author="cmenzel" created="Mon, 14 May 2012 16:18:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in 1.5.x and master.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m detecting external redirects and simply stop processing the request at that point. WicketTester has a new method #assertRedirectUrl that allows to check for a correct redirect.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;No compatibility issue, only one new public concrete method. The old failing behavior is a bug and prevented proper testing anyway.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
